data.description: Great home in the city of San Fernando area, perfect for a big family or rental income.  Main home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a bonus room.  Garage has been converted to a legal ADU with 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom.  Good size driveway to accommodate multiple cars.  Brand new storage shed in the backyard, great size lot to entertain.  Located close to supermarkets, shopping, main freeway, Blue Ribbon schools and entertainment.
